snippet.textDisplay: Broker's fees set up by the landlord are illegal, charging more than a $20 fee is also illegal no matter the price of rent. Also the landlord can only charge a security deposit equal to that of the rent. These are all laws that went into effect in 2020. No more paying a broker fee plus first and last months rent plus security. Don't get played, know your rights simply by an easy Google search.
